AGI doesn‚Äôt imply being smarter than all of humanity combined‚Äîthat‚Äôs the realm of Artificial Superintelligence (ASI). AGI simply means being smarter than any individual human, and I believe we‚Äôve already reached that point.

In fact, I‚Äôve found myself asking questions to my coworkers less frequently, as I now turn to these language models for answers. I‚Äôve also significantly reduced my reliance on Google and other traditional tools, opting instead to use LLMs for most of my information needs.

If you‚Äôre not convinced that Artificial General Intelligence (AGI) is already here, it‚Äôs likely because you haven‚Äôt fully explored how to effectively use the best language models available today. Models like GPT-4, Claude, Grok, and Gemini are far more intelligent than anyone I know. 

AGI doesn‚Äôt imply being smarter than all of humanity combined‚Äîthat‚Äôs the realm of Artificial Superintelligence (ASI). AGI simply means being smarter than any individual human, and I believe we‚Äôve already reached that point.

In fact, I‚Äôve found myself asking questions to my coworkers less frequently, as I now turn to these language models for answers. I‚Äôve also significantly reduced my reliance on Google and other traditional tools, opting instead to use LLMs for most of my information needs.
